flowchart TD
    A[AI System Anomaly Detected] --> B{Severity Assessment}
    B -->|Low| C[Log and Monitor]
    C --> D[Review at Next Cadence]
    B -->|Medium| E[Alert Model Owner]
    E --> F{Containable?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Apply Threshold Override]
    G --> H[Document and Update Risk Register]
    F -->|No| I[Escalate to Leadership]
    B -->|High| I
    I --> J{Immediate Harm Risk?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Activate Kill Switch]
    K --> L[Revert to Fallback System]
    L --> M[Post-Incident Review]
    J -->|No| N[Convene Cross-Functional Response]
    N --> O[Scenario-Based Remediation]
    O --> M
    M --> P[Update Risk Register and Protocols]